com.google.closure.plugin.common

Class Sources.Source

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.closure.plugin.common.Sources.Source
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Sources.Source>
    Enclosing class:
    Sources

    public static final class Sources.Source
extends Object
implements Comparable<Sources.Source>, Serializable
    A source path. In the following directory structure, 
     foo/
   bar → symlink to /baz
 baz/
   boo.txt
    A traversal which follows symlinks from foo looking for *.txt files would find a single Source:
     {
   canonicalPath :"/baz/boo.txt",
   originalPath: "/foo/bar/boo.txt",
   root: "/foo",
   relativePath: "bar/boo.txt",
 }
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
